        "solution": "\n \t\t\t<div class=\"solution-grid\">\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Datos</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-sm\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>P = 50.000 um</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>&pi; anual = 0,05</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>r anual = 0,12</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Fórmula</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"formula !my-2\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?i_f = (1+r)(1+\\pi)-1\" />\n \t\t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-span-full\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Desarrollo</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm\">Calculamos la tasa corriente anual: <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?i_{f_{anual}} = (1+0,12)(1+0,05)-1 = 0,176\" />. Convertimos a tasa semestral: <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?i_{f_{semestral}} = (1+0,176)^{(1/2)}-1 = 0,0844\" />.</p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"result-box\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"font-bold\">Resultado: Tasa corriente semestral = <strong>8,44%</strong></p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t</div>\n \t\t"
