        "solution": "\n \t\t\t<div class=\"solution-grid\">\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Datos</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-sm\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>TEA corriente = 0,10</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>&pi; anual = 0,04</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Fórmula</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"formula !my-2\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?r=\\frac{i_{f}-\\pi}{1+\\pi}\" />\n \t\t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-span-full\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Desarrollo</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm\">Convertimos las tasas anuales a trimestrales. <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?i_{f_{trimestral}}=(1+0,10)^{(1/4)}-1=0,02411\" />. <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?\\pi_{trimestral}=(1+0,04)^{(1/4)}-1=0,00985\" />. Calculamos la tasa real trimestral: <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?r = \\frac{0,02411 - 0,00985}{1+0,00985} = 0,01412\" />.</p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"result-box\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"font-bold\">Resultado: r trimestral = <strong>1,41%</strong></p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t</div>\n \t\t"
