        "solution": "\n \t\t\t<div class=\"solution-grid\">\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Datos</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-sm\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>FC Corriente = 1,200 um</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>&pi; anual = 0,06</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>n = 1 año</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Fórmula</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"formula !my-2\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?FC_{real} = \\frac{FC_{corriente}}{(1+\\pi)^n}\" />\n \t\t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-span-full\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Desarrollo</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm\">Deflactamos el flujo de caja corriente: <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?FC_{real} = \\frac{1200}{(1+0,06)^1} = 1132,08\" />.</p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"result-box\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"font-bold\">Resultado: FC Real = <strong>1.132,08 um</strong></p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t</div>\n \t\t"
