        "solution": "\n \t\t\t<div class=\"solution-grid\">\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Datos</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-sm\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>FC₁=5000, FC₂=5000, FC₃=5000</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<li>&pi; anual = 0,06</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Fórmula</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"formula !my-2\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?VP = \\sum \\frac{FC_{corriente}}{(1+\\pi)^n}\" />\n \t\t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-span-full\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"font-semibold\">Desarrollo</h5>\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm\">Calculamos el valor presente de cada flujo real: <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?VP = \\frac{5000}{(1,06)^1} + \\frac{5000}{(1,06)^2} + \\frac{5000}{(1,06)^3} = 4716,98 + 4449,98 + 4198,10 = 13365,06\" />.</p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t\t<div class=\"result-box\">\n \t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"font-bold\">Resultado: VP = <strong>13.365,06 um</strong></p>\n \t\t\t\t</div>\n \t\t\t</div>\n \t\t"
